%section
  %h3 Wireframes
  %p.note
    Wireframes are schematical draws of a website. They can be done on paper or
    with design software, and can be very rough or detailed, depending on the needs
    of the design&nbsp;process.
  %p.note
    They focus on information arrangement and are helpful to quickly share ideas
    with team members and clients. They will lead visual design and development.
